Are you an Enterprise Data Architect in the area of Amsterdam? Then we're looking for you!
One of our brand new clients is starting their business in Amsterdam and has an IT greenfield. In this position you are responsible for defining and managing the enterprise
wide data architecture and associated applications. The role works across IT and
business to ensure a cohesive, integrated strategy for management of the company’s data assets. In this role you are responsible for the development and maintenance of all data assets for the company including any operational databases, data warehouse, business intelligence, analytics and management reporting platforms. The Enterprise Data Architect also defines the strategy and architecture for data aggregation and integration platforms.
